# https://blog.stallmer.com/posts/posteo-imap-in-mutt/
IMAPStore posteo-remote
Host posteo.de
Port 993
User adam.dickison@posteo.net
#PassCmd ""
TLSType IMAPS
CertificateFile /etc/ssl/certs/ca-certificates.crt

MaildirStore posteo-local
Path ~/.local/mail/posteo
Inbox ~/.local/mail/posteo/INBOX
Subfolders Verbatim

Channel posteo
Far :posteo-remote:
Near :posteo-local:
Create Both
Expunge Both
SyncState *
Patterns *
